section.para:
If you start seeing java.sql.SQLException: Listener refused the connection with the following error: ORA-12519, TNS:no appropriate service handler found, there are a couple of things that may remedy the problem.
Increase the Oracle XE connection limit: alter system set processes=150 scope=spfile; alter system set sessions=150 scope=spfile;
Lower the pool size in your rice config.xml: <param name="datasource.pool.maxSize">10</param>
